==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Minge
<hw>Minge</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prob. corrupt. fr.
<ets>midge</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small biting fly; a
midge.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

